[[File:Provincia de La Grita.PNG|thumb|right|La Grita Province]]
'''La Grita Province''' was a [[province]] of the [[Spanish Empire]] in the 17th century (1576–1607), with [[La Grita]] (founded 1573) as its capital. In 1607 it merged with [[Mérida, Mérida|Mérida]] to form what became known as [[Mérida Province (Spanish Empire)|Mérida Province]].

