This is a list of Monuments in [[Kathmandu]] Metropolis -11, officially recognized by and available through the website of the [[Department of Archaeology (Nepal)|Department of Archaeology, Nepal]] in the [[Kathmandu District]].<ref name=monumentact>{{cite book |last=Government of Nepal, Law Books Management Committee |first= |date=1956 |title=प्राचीन स्मारक संरक्षण ऐन २०१३ |trans-title=Ancient Monument Protection Act 1956 |url=http://www.lawcommission.gov.np/?workflow_state=prevailing-laws-statutes-acts |language=ne |location=Kathmandu |publisher=Government of Nepal, Law Books Management Committee |isbn=}}</ref><ref name=monumentrule>{{cite book |last=His Majesty's Government of Nepal, Law Books Management Committee |first= |date=1990 |title=प्राचीन स्मारक संरक्षण नियमावली २०४६ |trans-title=Ancient Monument Protection Rule 1990 |url=http://www.tourism.gov.np/downloadfile/16_1503552999.pdf|language=ne |location=Kathmandu |publisher=His Majesty's Government of Nepal, Law Books Management Committee |isbn=}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book |url=https://books.google.com.np/books?id=-hQkAAAAMAAJ&q=Monuments+in+Kathmandu&dq=Monuments+in+Kathmandu&hl=en&sa=X&redir_esc=y |title=Kathmandu Valley: Nepalese Historic Monuments in Need of Preservation |last=Sanday |first=John |date=1982 |publisher=Bernan Assoc |isbn=9789231019920 |language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book |url=https://books.google.com.np/books?id=eFPF3cr7RIQC&pg=PA153&dq=Monuments+in+Kathmandu&hl=en&sa=X&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q=Monuments%2520in%2520Kathmandu&f=false |title=Journey to Kathmandu |last=Oliphant |first=Laurence |date=1994 |publisher=Asian Educational Services |isbn=9788120609419 |language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book |url=https://books.google.com.np/books?id=UWKTmJ8iR84C&pg=PA160&dq=Monuments+in+Kathmandu&hl=en&sa=X&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q=Monuments%2520in%2520Kathmandu&f=false |title=Asian Heritage Management: Contexts, Concerns, and Prospects |last=Silva |first=Kapila D. |last2=Chapagain |first2=Neel Kamal |date=2013-03-05 |publisher=Routledge |isbn=9781135075613 |language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book |url=https://books.google.com.np/books?id=rCluAAAAMAAJ&q=Monuments+in+Kathmandu&dq=Monuments+in+Kathmandu&hl=en&sa=X&redir_esc=y |title=Kathmandu City |last=Finsterwalder |first=Rüdiger |last2=Höfer |first2=András |last3=Gutschow |first3=Niels |date=1979 |publisher=Universitätsverlag Wagner |language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book |url=https://books.google.com.np/books?id=iZFPAQAAMAAJ&q=%25E0%25A4%25A8%25E0%25A5%2587%25E0%25A4%25AA%25E0%25A4%25BE%25E0%25A4%25B2%25E0%25A4%2595%25E0%25A4%25BE+%25E0%25A4%25B8%25E0%25A4%25BE%25E0%25A4%2582%25E0%25A4%25B8%25E0%25A5%258D%25E0%25A4%2595%25E0%25A5%2583%25E0%25A4%25A4%25E0%25A4%25BF%25E0%25A4%2595+%25E0%25A4%25A7%25E0%25A4%25B0%25E0%25A5%258B%25E0%25A4%25B9%25E0%25A4%25B0%25E0%25A4%25B9%25E0%25A4%25B0%25E0%25A5%2582&dq=%25E0%25A4%25A8%25E0%25A5%2587%25E0%25A4%25AA%25E0%25A4%25BE%25E0%25A4%25B2%25E0%25A4%2595%25E0%25A4%25BE+%25E0%25A4%25B8%25E0%25A4%25BE%25E0%25A4%2582%25E0%25A4%25B8%25E0%25A5%258D%25E0%25A4%2595%25E0%25A5%2583%25E0%25A4%25A4%25E0%25A4%25BF%25E0%25A4%2595+%25E0%25A4%25A7%25E0%25A4%25B0%25E0%25A5%258B%25E0%25A4%25B9%25E0%25A4%25B0%25E0%25A4%25B9%25E0%25A4%25B0%25E0%25A5%2582&hl=en&sa=X&redir_esc=y |title=Viśva sampadā sūcīmā Nepālakā sampadāharū |date=2000 |publisher=Śrī 5 ko Sarakāra, Sūcanā tathā Sañcāra Mantrālaya, Sūcanā Vibhāga |language=ne}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book |url=https://books.google.com.np/books?id=SFQFPNUZ2WMC&q=%25E0%25A4%25A8%25E0%25A5%2587%25E0%25A4%25AA%25E0%25A4%25BE%25E0%25A4%25B2%25E0%25A4%2595%25E0%25A4%25BE+%25E0%25A4%25B8%25E0%25A4%25BE%25E0%25A4%2582%25E0%25A4%25B8%25E0%25A5%258D%25E0%25A4%2595%25E0%25A5%2583%25E0%25A4%25A4%25E0%25A4%25BF%25E0%25A4%2595+%25E0%25A4%25A7%25E0%25A4%25B0%25E0%25A5%258B%25E0%25A4%25B9%25E0%25A4%25B0%25E0%25A4%25B9%25E0%25A4%25B0%25E0%25A5%2582&dq=%25E0%25A4%25A8%25E0%25A5%2587%25E0%25A4%25AA%25E0%25A4%25BE%25E0%25A4%25B2%25E0%25A4%2595%25E0%25A4%25BE+%25E0%25A4%25B8%25E0%25A4%