==Calling formats== To call in Ivory Coast, the following format is used: * '''yy xxxxxx''' - calls within [[Ivory Coast]] * '''+225 yy xxxxxx''' - calls from outside [[Ivory Coast]] to a landline
* '''+225 yy xxxxxx''' - calls from outside [[Ivory Coast]] to a mobile number
