[[Curaçao]] requires its residents to register their [[motor vehicle]]s and display '''[[vehicle registration plate]]s'''.<ref>http://www.worldlicenseplates.com/world/CA_CURA.html</ref> Current plates are [[Vehicle_registration_plates_of_the_United_States#Designs_and_serial_formats|North American standard]] 6 × 12 inches (152 × 300 mm).<ref>http://www.plateshack.com/y2k/Curacao/curacaoy2k.htm</ref> Some plates start with different letters, sometimes similar to [[Vehicle_registration_plates_of_the_Netherlands|plates of the Netherlands]]: V for commercial vehicles, TX for taxi, D for governmental vehicles, AB for buses.
